{"word":"διαδρομή","slug":"διαδρομή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαδρομή</b></el> <el>(διαδρομή, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>διαδραμεῖν</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a running about through</i> a city, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a foray</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a passage through</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>: <i>an aqueduct</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}